{"tid":2501414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"捷克再下令幾十名俄羅斯外交人員限時離境","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:45:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"345b491ce22647f81181df7bc082b84237632a7d","tid":2501414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587334-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587334-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=240d060a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587334-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=950f732f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587334-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克與俄羅斯的外交糾紛升級，捷克政府再下令幾十名俄羅斯駐布拉格大使館人員，必須在5月底前離境。<br />\n<br />\n捷克外長說，俄羅斯必須在5月底前，把大使館人員減至與捷克駐莫斯科大使館人數相同的24人。俄羅斯駐當地大使館現時有90多人。<br />\n<br />\n捷克政府早前驅逐18名俄國使館人員，指莫斯科牽涉當地2014年一宗釀成兩死的爆炸案。莫斯科隨後驅逐20名捷克外交人員報復。"}]}